### Java／Kotlin／Spring／Vert.x 项目常用 .gitattributes 模板 ###
### GitHub地址： https://github.com/yanwenkun/git-ignore-and-attributes-for-java ###
### 作者 yanwenkun@foxmail.com ###
### 版本 20191121-1 ###

# 自动检测文本文件并统一为LF行尾
* text=auto eol=lf

# 专有的Windows文件使用CRLF
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf

# 所有脚本与配置均使用LF换行
*.sh text eol=lf
*.conf text eol=lf
*.properties text eol=lf
*.xml text eol=lf
*.java text eol=lf
*.jsp text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.map text eol=lf
*.kt text eol=lf
*.kts text eol=lf

# 二级制文件不做修改
*.doc binary
*.docx binary
*.xls binary
*.xlsx binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.svg binary
*.ttf binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.eot binary
